<plot>After coming out as gay and HIV positive Michael Kearns hollywood career dried up. He then developed a one man play, Intimacies wherein he plays twelve PWA's (persons with AIDS) of various races and cultures. This is the story of the man, that play and what's coming next.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?267325</url></doc>
